    "description": "<p>Orchard Rendezvous Hotel by Far East Hospitality</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Orchard Rendezvous Hotel’s blend of rich historical references and delightful botanical touches provide a welcome retreat for both business and leisure travellers. All the rooms have the luxury of space for guests to relax and unwind after a long day of shopping, where the 37-63sqm Family Rooms are ideal for families.</p>\n<p>Conveniently located at the beginning of Orchard Road, Orchard Rendezvous Hotel is a short walk from the MRT station and the ideal starting point to explore Singapore’s iconic shopping street. For the nature lovers, UNESCO World Heritage Site of Singapore Botanic Gardens is only a 5-minute drive away.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Food lovers will also be spoilt for choice with the wide selection of dining options in the immediate area that span local cafés all the way to Chinese and Western restaurants. With so many shopping, dining, and entertainment choices at your doorstep, Orchard Rendezvous Hotel is the place to stay to experience the best Singapore has to offer.</p>",
